prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor painting illustration for a birthday greeting card front, featuring two cartoon characters based on the reference photo [37e14119-ff1f-47ba-a4e1-e72bd3757ec4]. The characters, an older woman and a younger man, are depicted in a funny, lighthearted scene, bursting with laughter while trying to assemble a piece of furniture with exaggeratedly confused expressions and holding tools upside down. They highly resemble the people in the photo, maintaining their exact hairstyles, facial features, clothing (without text/logos), and body proportions. The scene is set against a clean, bright white background, emphasizing the characters. In the center, the text "Happy Birthday to the Lao Lao who can do it all... eventually!" is written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script. The artwork is a flat 2D design, rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds. --ar 5:7 --style raw

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
